FINAL RULE



End rhyme gives the wall shape.

Internal rhyme gives it wiring.

Mosaic rhyme shows craftsmanship.

Beat-shift rhyme gives it swagger.

Drift keeps it alive.



We are not decorating lyrics.



We are building load-bearing sound.



